        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_OVERHEAT_MASO": "<style=cKeywordName>Overheat: Masochism</style>If Arsonist leaves Masochism due to excessive heat buildup, EX Overheat is applied, reducing Movement Speed and Damage to 70%. Canceling or letting the skill run its course applies Overheat, reducing Attack Speed to 50%.",
